# 301 every request landing on the pages.dev preview URL to the canonical
# domain. Cloudflare Pages honors full-URL source matches in _redirects, so
# sealstack.ai traffic is unaffected — only sealstack-docs.pages.dev is.
#
# The trailing `!` is "force", meaning the redirect fires even when a file
# exists at the same path — required since the build output itself is what
# serves on the pages.dev hostname.

https://sealstack-docs.pages.dev/* https://sealstack.ai/:splat 301!
